These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, italian, japanese, thai, turkish
House: tower, modern, craftsman, townhouse, futuristic, colonial, farmhouse
 1. the australian is between the italian and the turkish##2
 2. the french is in the middle##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the japanese is between the craftsman house and the futuristic house##2
 5. the modern house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 6. the modern house is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the tower house is between the townhouse house and the craftsman house##2
 8. the modern house is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the thai##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the craftsman house##1
11. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | italian | australian | turkish | french    | indonesian | japanese   | thai    |
| House         | colonial  | modern   | townhouse | tower | craftsman   | farmhouse | futuristic |

