.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, ship, taxi, jet-ski, train, quad-bike, van
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Transport   | van | train | trike | ship   | jet-ski | taxi | quad-bike |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

