.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, prince, bolivar, tiparillo, davidoff, chaman
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the chaman-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the bolivar-smoker##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Cigar   | bolivar      | tiparillo | vegafina | prince | chaman      | aristoff      | davidoff |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

