4. the paramedic is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching crime movies and the firefighter##2
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
