 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the electrician##1
 7. the manager is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the journalist##1
 9. the chef is between the journalist and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

