There are 7 different favourite colors: azure, lilac, orange, ivory, purple, apricot, chestnut
 1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
 7. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade   | cola         | fanta     | water              | mirinda    | juice     |
| Color        | apricot | lilac | purple | ivory | chestnut | azure | orange |

