The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the person traveling to paris is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| City   | marseilles | boston     | colone | new-york | venice | miami  | paris |
| Transport     | quad-bike | skateboard | taxi   | bus     | trike    | motorbike | tram   |

