 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of pop is the person driving the helicopter##1

