.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-14::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, pony, chinchilla, lizard, hedgehog, guinea-pig
There 7 different types of food: apricot, banana, carrot, kiwi, lemon, orange, spinach
 1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
