 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person eating carrot is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person eating orange##1
 8. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating carrot##2
10. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Pet   | chinchilla   | pony | rabbit | bird   | lizard   | hedgehog     | guinea-pig  |
| Food       | apricot | lemon    | kiwi  | orange | banana | spinach | carrot |

