 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person eating corn is the person eating corn##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating corn is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | adventure | romance      | documentary | animation       | martial-arts | horror |
